<P><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">, which appears the mo&s;t plau&s;i<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">le of <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hey h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ve p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">j<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">t<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d is received wi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">h the g<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">eate&s;t partialit<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> by our far|mer<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, is, never <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">, contra|dicted by <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he con&s;ta<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t experie<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ce of the grea<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e&s;t and the mo&s;t a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ci|ent la<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d-labou<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ing <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> in the world, who r<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">gard the practice of meadow<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">d f<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">l<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">owing g<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ou<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ds, as an abu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e, de&s;tructive of plenty and p<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">pula<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ion, w<G